♪Wandering in the world♪

276
00:11:32,630 --> 00:11:35,150
♪Braving the storms♪

277
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:37,510
♪Destiny twists and turns♪

278
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:39,710
♪I'm trapped in a web of intrigue♪

279
00:11:39,710 --> 00:11:42,150
♪My eyes reflect the cold world♪

280
